Definition: the part of the occipital cortex that receives the fibers of the optic radiation from the lateral geniculate body and is the primary receptive area for vision
Synonyms: striate_area, first_visual_area, area_, _of_Brodmann, Brodmann, s_area_, cortical_area, occipital_lobe, p, the, part, of, occipital, cortex, that, receives, fibers, optic, radiation, from, lateral, geniculate, body, and, is, primary, receptive, area, for, vision
Category: noun.body
